Package: ggthemer
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Module for ggplot2 Theme Modification
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Dzmitry G Batrakou
Maintainer: Dzmitry G Batrakou <d.batrakou@gmail.com>
Description: ggthemer is a Shiny module for modifying components of ggplot2 themes.
    It provides two main functions, `ggthemerUI` that will generate user interface 
    and `ggthemerSERV` which is the server part of the module.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends:
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    shinyBS
Imports:
    stats,
    tools,
    htmltools,
    grDevices,
    shinyjs,
    colourpicker,
    shinyWidgets,
    showtext,
    sysfonts
    
